videos.description: Udoka Azubuike spins around his defender and throws down the two-handed slam
videos.headline: Kansas' Azubuike post moves lead to slam

videos.description: Sviatoslav Mykhailiuk chases down Kouat Noi and denies him a breakaway dunk.
videos.headline: Kansas' Mykhailiuk patrols the rim

videos.description: Devonte' Graham penetrates to the basket and finds Udoka Azubuike for the nice slam.
videos.headline: Jayhawks' Graham-Azubuike connection leads to dunk

videos.description: JD Miller takes the outlet pass and throws down the tomahawk slam.
videos.headline: TCU's Miller gets flashy in transition

videos.description: Mitch Lightfoot stays in front of TCU's Jaylen Fisher then blocks his 3-point attempt.
videos.headline: Jayhawks' Lightfoot makes huge play on defense
